### Database — [schema.prisma](file:///j:/PaceUp/prisma/schema.prisma)

6 models with proper indexing:

| Model | Key Fields | Notes |
|-------|-----------|-------|
| `User` | clerkId, skills[], domains[], level | Unique on clerkId |
| `Group` | name, inviteCode, createdById | Unique on inviteCode |
| `GroupMember` | groupId, userId, role | Compound unique (groupId, userId) — allows multi-group |
| `ProjectBrief` | groupId, ideaStatement, deadline, status | Unique on groupId (1:1 via reverse relation) |
| `Task` | projectBriefId, assignedUserId, status | Status pipeline: NOT_STARTED → IN_PROGRESS → DONE / OVERDUE |
| `AIKey` | userId, provider, encryptedKey, isActive | Compound unique (userId, provider) — AES-256-GCM encrypted |

