| [/api/ai/assign-tasks](file:///j:/PaceUp/app/api/ai/assign-tasks/route.ts) | POST | AI-powered role + task assignment with retry logic |
| [/api/tasks/:id](file:///j:/PaceUp/app/api/tasks/[id]/route.ts) | PATCH | Update task status (owner only, validated transitions) |
